game.name: Frozen Elsa Birth Caring
game.description:
The biggest day has come in the life of your favorite princess Frozen Elsa. She got pregnant and is expected to deliver a cute baby boy today. She has managed to call the ambulance and reach to her nearest hospital where delivery will take place. Luckily, a cute baby boy was born in the operation theatre. But, a tragedy has occurred suddenly and her doctor left the operation room urgently. Being her best friend and a good doctor, you have taken the responsibility to take care of her baby now in Frozen Elsa Birth Caring game. 

Your objective in this brand new doctor game is to cut the umbilical cord of her baby, listen to his heartbeat and complete all the series of check-ups to ensure a safe delivery. Breastfeeding will also be your responsibility to pamper her baby. Be careful and perform all the medical procedures for the safety of the princess and her new born baby in this one of the best surgical games for girls! Wrap him up with a blanket before putting him on his bed!

Clean baby with a soft baby towel, give him a needful injection and measure his weight through the weighting machine in this one of the top girls games! Her husband also looks pretty excited to see his first baby. Go through the baby under a routine check up and make some basic measurements to know if everything is ok and then put him in the arms of her mother for breastfeeding! Enjoy a lot in major titles from the category of Frozen girls games, without download!
